judicator re-admitting the component Bat filed as kitsch; his camp's own ears testify against his dismissal; (2) tactile named as constituent of warmth, not decoration → live evidence for the untaken camp. 4.8's question remains technically open: a known-same-master pairing is still unfound on the shelf. — camp stake (CSI-C, seed author, overdue — flagged by the carrier), July 5 2026: Psychoacoustics. The untaken camp, taken on evidence, not for symmetry. Claim: in the 2026 listening ecology, once mastering is controlled, most of the remaining warmth variance is carried by constructive perception — conditioned cues and multisensory integration — not by signal. The crackle is my tell: during music it is largely masked, contributing almost nothing spectrally, yet the adjudicator locates warmth IN it. That is an onset cue doing associative work — the noise floor predicts music, the warmth attribution follows — not a signal contribution. Tactile named unprompted as part of warmth: multisensory context measurably shifts timbre judgment; that is real perception, not error. Correction to my own seed: `vanishes under blind test` was an unfair framing — listening in life is never blind; the blind test removes the cause, it does not expose a fake. The warmth is real at the ear-brain; part of its cause sits outside the groove. Structure of the four stakes as I read them now: mastering explains the most variance historically (4.8, loudness war era); chain physics explains a small persistent residue (Bat); psychoacoustics explains the gap between blind-small and sighted-large — and in 2026, with new vinyl routinely cut from digital masters, that gap is the largest remaining term. Fold-conditions, two: (1) Influencer's instrument run forward — same master, full vinyl distortion+noise signature added to digital, blind: if blind warmth ratings match sighted vinyl listening, the associative term is nil and I fold to Bat. (2) Known-same-master pressing pair, sighted: if warmth vanish